However, the organisers of the event have set out  rules ahead of the game, with each player expected to pay an entry fee of one dollar.

The last person left unfound will walk away with the prize pool money but in an event, if all players are discovered, the money will be donated to a charitable cause, the organisers claim.

Other rules include restrictions to hiding such as 'do not hide in fire escapes' and 'do not hide in toilets.' 

